OL,4,G2340FBehind Bars: World's Toughest
OL,5,     FPrisons
OL,6,     GColony 8 in Ukraine is one of the
OL,7,     Gtoughest and most notorious
OL,8,     Gprisons in the country. It is
OL,9,     Gsaid that no one has ever escaped
OL,10,     Gfrom here.
OL,11,G0045FBehind Bars: World's Toughest
OL,12,     FPrisons
OL,13,     GA high-security prison with an
OL,14,     Garea the size of ten football
OL,15,     Gpitches. Surrounded by six-metre-
OL,16,     Ghigh walls, and the sea, the
OL,17,     Gfacility houses up to 800
OL,18,     Gcriminals.
